| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-5934 — Recovery Inhibition (raworld)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: e4254f8c-e6a4-50ff-8258-71bbd9dba2ba"
